-- Reliance Industries `Not in a Hurry' to Form New Shale Gas Partnerships
-- B y   R a k t e e m   K a t a k e y   a n d   P r a t i k   P a r i j a
-- 2010-10-31T09:14:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-31/reliance-not-in-a-hurry-to-form-new-shale-gas-partnerships.html
Reliance Industries Ltd. is “not in
a hurry” to form new shale gas partnerships and is focussed on
consolidating existing ventures, Alok Agarwal, chief financial
officer, said in a conference call with reporters today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
